
start.html - welcome message
           - form has text box for credits
           - calls status.php

status.php - done before <html>
           - get credits from GET array
           - set credits cookie

           - done in <html>
           - form has radio buttons for status
           - calls state.php

state.php - done before <html>
          - get status from GET array
          - set status cookie

          - done in <html>
          - form has radio buttons for state
          - calls calculate.php

calculate.php - get credits from cookie
              - get status from cookie
              - get state from GET array
 
              - compute cost
              - display inputs and cost
              - button link to start.html
              - <a href="start.html"><button>Start over</button></a>
